outputs.output_descr: This project is part of the UNDP country programme action that applies an area-based approach to development in the Fergana Valley. It focuses on three key and inter-linked areas: support for market reform within the WIS and MDG process, rural development as well as private sector development.

project_descr:
Regional/local institutions are strengthened to conceive and implement employment
generation and poverty reduction initiatives in Fergana Valley that are sustainable, effective and gender responsive.
project_title: Enhancement of Living Standards in Ferghana Valley
